Package: likertSim
Title: Likert Simulation with Polychoric Option and Stress Knobs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("TM", "Tauseef Mamun", email = "tauseefim@yahoo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simulates Likert ratings using empirical thresholds, polychoric
    correlation structure (with Pearson fallback), and stress knobs for noise,
    bias, and correlation weakening. Includes a wrapper function
    simulate_and_compare() for direct use.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
